data.title: Chetna - Singh - Microsoft
data.meta_description: CHETNA_SINGH_ MICROSOFT - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Microsoft Corporation is a multinational technology company headquartered in Redmond, Washington. It develops, manufactures, licenses, and supports software, services, devices, and solutions. Some of Microsoft's most popular products include Windows, Office, Xbox, Bing and Azure. The company aims to put a computer in every home and desktop, running Microsoft software. It has faced antitrust lawsuits and criticism over monopolistic practices but remains highly successful with a focus on continual innovation.
